{
  "stem": "8892.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The next day is Sunday, the church bell going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the people are going to church.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, the Jews are in their synagogue, already gathered.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And thinking back now, I started to talk to my brother-- my cousin about it-- that recollect my thought that they didn't do it while church was going on, that the Gentiles cannot see us, but they did like two o'clock afternoon.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The wagons would show up with the gendarme on it and gather everybody.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You were allowed to stay together as families.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So as many of us can-- we were six of us-- so we took care of one wagon.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Oh, I have to track back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the meantime this is going on, Saturday afternoon, my brother from Budapest, the oldest one, Laszlo, shows up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, we thought-- mother was thrilled to see here son-- but we thought this was the end of the world.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He did not know when they gave him a furlough, because he was legally drafted with the Hungarian-- it was an army already-- that was just labor camp, but drafting, OK?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Had to appear at that so-and-so station, and they gave him three days furlough to go home to say goodbye to the parents.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By that time, we gathered already to go to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He does not know that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is no communication, nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't even know what happened to them in our whole two weeks or so.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And no mail came, nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So when my brother shows up, and he sees what's going on, he does not want to go back.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
